					li At the second exit to Garson, turn north on Road 33E.
					li Drive approximately 5 km on Road 33E.
					li Hawthorn Estates is the second driveway on your left after crossing the 3rd mile road.
	#hawthorn.map

	section
		.row
			.small-12.medium-6.small-centered.columns
